column5: I'll be getting my 1st tattoo in less then 2 hrs  , a smallie on the back of my right leg my 2 sons go tomorrow & Friday for theirs, same smallie different lure  , any one else got fish tattoos, 50 only comes once I guess Richard
Wow, if your sons are 50, you must be REALLY old!
I had this done in London at Perfect Image. Its not a fish but a Gamagatsu walleye wide gap hook, my fav for spinner rigs.      Its my one and only tattoo......     TDunn
Probably most important, is what lure is it going to be hooked with?

It's your first??  I can bet that it won't be your last.  TDunn nice one!!  Here's mine,  would've been too redneck if I got it done in English  It says I LOVE FISHING   That's my 5th one and I am looking at getting more.  The next one will be the outline of my childhood lake where I first started fishing.
Wont be your last i promise................
That looks awesome.  I often threaten my wife that I'm going to get a giant jumping brookie tattooed across my back, but I think I'd be getting divorced.
my buddy has the gloomis fish skeleton logo on his back, looks pretty darn sweet!  and my buddies brother has the fear no fish on the back of his shoulder
